r\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5a1facf8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5a1facf8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6b9c8e89 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6b9c8e89\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"720\" height=\"405\" src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/result-1-1.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-3619\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/result-1-1.webp 720w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/result-1-1-300x169.webp 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-50bb3306 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"50bb3306\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8e23b2d elementor-widget__width-auto sub-title elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8e23b2d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">DIGNITY FOR DEAD WOMEN\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1cc79411 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1cc79411\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In consultation with a coalition of domestic violence experts and victims\u2019 families, Level Up produced the UK\u2019s first media guidelines on how to report domestic abuse deaths. They are endorsed by both press regulators IPSO and IMPRESS.<\/p><p>Level Up has trained over 500 journalists in how to report fatal domestic abuse, using our guidelines and a four-point acronym AIDA (Accountability, Images, Dignity, Accuracy).<\/p><p>If you are interested in booking a CPD-accredited training for yourself or your newsroom, please contact\u00a0<em><a class=\"c-link\" href=\"mailto:mediasupport@welevelup.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-stringify-link=\"mailto:mediasupport@welevelup.org\" data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\" aria-haspopup=\"menu\">mediasupport@welevelup.org<\/a><\/em><\/p><p>Working with victims\u2019 families, Level Up produced research into the impact of media reporting on families\u2019 bereavement in the aftermath of a domestic abuse death. The majority of families who participated said their grieving process was negatively impacted by media reporting.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6ca6a285 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"6ca6a285\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/levelup.yourmovement.org\/p\/dignity-for-dead-women\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">SIGN THE PETITION<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elemen